<plot>Kyle Green is a boy who cannot speak and suffers from an uncommon condition that causes him to have a severe weakness in cold temperatures. His peculiar disease creates tension between family members and rips them apart. When a greedy doctor discovers something special about Kyle - he kidnaps the boy and leaves the family desperate to save him. Getting Kyle back may be the only way to bring this family back together.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?590794</url></doc>
